Description: The Coffee Shop at TI offers casual dining at its finest. Just off the main casino floor, The Coffee Shop provides a warm and relaxed atmosphere with a stunning view of the tropical pool, and al fresco patio dining option. With a diverse menu ranging from traditional comfort foods to more eclectic fare, this restaurant is the perfect choice for breakfast, lunch or dinner.
Location: 3300 S Las Vegas Blvd, Las Vegas, NV 89109
